channel.title: MESG Product Update - Nov '19
channel.description:
This month marks the release of the Engine v0.17, decentralized executions, an updated Marketplace website, and a migration to a JavaScript mono-repo.

This is a companion discussion topic for the original entry at https://blog.mesg.com/product-update-nov-19/
